				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just a quick tidbit of information I (finally) tracked down on the www.kadanit.com/eqmonks site.  Instill doubt, for those of you who have been wondering, is supposed to cause the mob you are facing to turn tail and run, much like the fear spell.  From what I've heard, it rarely works, but hey, sounds neat anyways.  Another tidbit - When you get to level 10 or so, or you have some travelling companions, I would suggest the Cat's Isle (between Qeynos and Erudin) as a great place to hunt, but bring your magic gloves.  Wisps all over the place!
